column12:
'desc': [u'

Piyo Piyo Anti-bacterial Baby Wipes (80 Pieces) Price: Rs.290

Wet wipes can be used as a good alternative to washing with water when cleaning your infant’s skin. After every diaper change if you wash your little one’s tush there are chances of the baby contracting infections and rashes due to the depletion of essential oils from the skin. These Antibacterial\xa0 Baby Wipes from Piyo Piyo are enhanced with RO pure water that makes the wipes mild on a newborn’s skin. Made of imported rayon Piyo Piyo Antibacterial Wipes are thick and will be gentle in cleansing the skin of dirt and germs.\xa0Enriched with moisturizing agent and plant extracts these Antibacterial Wipes will keep the skin adequately hydrated and supple.

The resealable cover of these wet wipes will allow you to keep them tightly closed after use and thus the moisture in the wipes will be retained in them.

']
